017%2F10%2F11%2F084521_dd6741b1c44fee8dcb5835f9fa0fb89e.jpg&h=e50010cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我已經等左佢3日 仲未更新完<br />\n<br />\n如果其他人都有呢個問題<br />\n我就回報bug <br />\n冇既我就攞去整<br />\n<br />\n利申： iPhone 8</blockquote><br />\n第三點，試下向下再拉，迫佢更新個進度"},{"pid":"e1a2490b6c2cea22901739ea9c93e0d82e1c415d","tid":431603,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:54:20.000Z","msg":"3.更新一次要熄機一次先更新到<br />\n唔係就會停係呢個畫面<br />\n<br />\n呢個真係bug到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫人整過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3458053b2e8f5aeb3f402d7eae23e04518424b40","tid":431603,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第3個試過 肯定bugs黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238c523b3dbe9d3f18625436718dac0f6687babc","tid":431603,"uid":143305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"Apple已死"},{"pid":"36e793cd5530b7817a6fe09175d743e500779b5d","tid":431603,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T11:19:21.000Z","msg":"我連apps都更新唔到"},{"pid":"9f8ea33df9aa6e6823d74e5fbce4fe95419e60bc","tid":431603,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T11:19:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我連apps都download 唔到</blockquote>"}]}